{"tid":1833850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如何成為立法會飲食界功能組別選民？","createTime":"2020-01-22T05:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T11:56:26.000Z","uid":47194,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ec5ba9fa769c61db7664d74e1a61eadbb328d2c2","tid":1833850,"uid":47194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E0DmR9S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE0DmR9S.jpg&h=db224302&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同行齊心 光復飲食界</span></strong><br />\n目前飲食界選民只有4685名(含團體票945及個人票3740)，現任議員張宇人由2000年起出任至今，當中2008年、2012年兩屆更是自動當選，今屆張宇人獲2438票，如按照上列條件登記，估計選民基數將以倍數增加，大家將可改變選舉形勢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要成為能組別飲食界選民，只需要符合下列條件當中一項即可：<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 從事飲食業的，並根據《公眾衞生及市政條例》（第132章）發出的食物業牌照的持有人<br />\n‧食肆牌照<br />\n‧食物製造廠牌照<br />\n‧烘製麵包餅食店牌照<br />\n‧工廠食堂牌照<br />\n‧燒味鹵味店牌照<br />\n‧新鮮糧食店牌照<br />\n‧冰凍及甜點製造廠牌照<br />\n‧奶品廠牌照<br />\n‧綜合食物店牌照<br />\n<br />\n2. 或是下列團體會員：<br />\n<strong>(一) 香港餐務管理協會有限公司</strong><br />\n九龍灣宏通街2號 寶康中心2字樓2F13室<br />\n電話： 2753 6703<br />\n<br />\n<strong>(二)現代管理(飲食)專業協會有限公司</strong><br />\n尖沙咀亞士厘道20號好利時大廈 2/F<br />\n電話： 2698 9344<br />\n<br />\n<strong>(三)香港飲食業總商會</strong><br />\n灣仔泰港大廈<br />\n電話：28912738<br />\n<br />\n<strong>(四)香港飲食業聯合總會有限公司</strong><br />\n觀塘勵業街46號天輝工業大廈<br />\n電話:2523 6128<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個人選民與/團體選民</span></strong><br />\n因上述工會可能有公司/團體會員與個人會員之分別，故有意成為選民的可選擇如下：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">個人</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(a) 請填寫表格REO-41（&ldquo;功能界別選民及／或選舉委員會界別分組投票人個人登記申請表&rdquo;）;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C%29.pdf&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=fbca22bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C).pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n(b) 申請登記在這個功能界別及一個選舉委員會界別分組。<br />\n如你想更改功能界別選民及/或選舉委員會界別分組投票人個人登記資料/取消登記或不登記於區議會(第二)功能界別申請表，請填寫REO-43<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-43(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-43%28C%29.pdf&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=c0e00513\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-43(C).pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">團體</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(b) 請填寫表格REO-42（&ldquo;功能界別選民及/或選舉委員會界別分組投票人團體登記/更改登記資料申請表&rdquo;）。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-42(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-42%28C%29.pdf&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=dd7516c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-42(C).pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n團體也可委任獲授權代表投票(只適用於團體)<br />\n獲授權代表的資格如下 ：<br />\n<br />\n(1) 已登記為地方選區選民，或有資格登記為地方選區選民，並已申請作如此登記及<br />\n(2) 與申請登記的團體有密切聯繫，例如獲授權代表是申請團體的成員、會員、合夥人、高級人員、人員或僱員。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新註冊選民請盡可能在5月2日前登記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原有「超級區議會」選民，請在4月1日前提交申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n當你登記為批發及零售界功能界別選民，將有權在立法會及選舉委員會界別分組換屆選舉或補選中投票：請記緊於如果你要在2020年9月在立法會選舉時，在飲食業功能組別上投票，你必須2020年5月2日前完成登記(原有「超級區議會」選民請在4月1日)，否則將不能投票。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過若你在2020年5月2日(4月1日)後才完成登記，仍可以參加2021年12月的選舉委員會投票，選出17名飲食屆選委，該等選委將可2022年行政長官選舉上投票。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a548aa1eb052765ad2d12d915bf132daa406a1fd","tid":1833850,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:51:04.000Z","msg":"註你老母，廢除呀"},{"pid":"6182918fd9ef95d4db5ed1ebbdff221ecc680328","tid":1833850,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:22:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6f460ed8a0f7bf6b669404d463ddad5833ec319d","tid":1833850,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T13:51:09.000Z","msg":"要開始全力推立法會"},{"pid":"10431126c949002ff13345e9c40d4a9a0d8500dc","tid":1833850,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a096d56166957f24cf350114cca3b5842d0368","tid":1833850,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:45:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d830161c77a719812d53855ec4acc58e86105e2b","tid":1833850,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T01:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bace9d0da6bb61a97a0cd8c7bd885195f6ddd2b","tid":1833850,"uid":124048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T01:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867d8e86405251662329dd14c99f0b8062b7f48f","tid":1833850,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T01:43:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ddcff99fec633338ba1df642fd96957e13b9d21","tid":1833850,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T01:43:38.000Z","msg":"姐係夠18歲就得？"},{"pid":"74f2152dab323bb37e48be1471ba2258393525a6","tid":1833850,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c616bc553ea2164a55bec9590f7799409e186ab7","tid":1833850,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99f390e18e58a85b1f733cf0860fa07e9bec325","tid":1833850,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}